Hi Tyson,

A friend of mine has managed to compile rtNEAT using gcc 4.1.2. Some
minor modifications were necessary.

If you want to play with it:  http://www.ime.usp.br/~cesargm/rtNEAT.1.0.tar.bz2

Just run make and then ./rtneat <experiment_settings>

[]'s
Cesar
